{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "02456271-617f-4dd2-a29c-fc7d5b314373", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/02456271-617f-4dd2-a29c-fc7d5b314373@4.pkg/1772602100770/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602101134", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/02456271-617f-4dd2-a29c-fc7d5b314373@4.pkg/1772602100770/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602101134"}, "identifier": "02456271-617f-4dd2-a29c-fc7d5b314373", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>本题考查对诗歌内容的理解能力。ABD．正确；C．有误，卖炭翁不敢反抗。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故选：C。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下面对《卖炭翁》一诗赏析</span><span class=\"dot\">不正确</span><span>的一项是（　　）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>卖炭翁</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中。满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营？身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歌。翩翩两骑来是谁？黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红绡一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下面对《卖炭翁》一诗赏析不正确的一项是（　　）卖炭翁卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中。满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营？身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歌。翩翩两骑来是谁？黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红绡一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/02456271-617f-4dd2-a29c-fc7d5b314373@4.pkg/item.json?v=1747213153424", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这首诗是一首讽喻诗，也是一首叙事诗，诗的主题在于揭露唐朝宫市的公开掠夺性。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>白居易是唐朝伟大的现实主义诗人，是新乐府运动的倡导者，他与唐代的李白、杜甫一样都是著名诗人。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>全诗完整地记述了卖炭老人烧炭、运炭和卖炭的经过，刻画了卖炭翁受压榨受欺凌但敢于反抗的人物形象。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中&rdquo;运用叙述，&ldquo;满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑&rdquo;则运用描写，全诗笔法简洁，富有表现力。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下面对《卖炭翁》一诗赏析</span><span class=\"dot\">不正确</span><span>的一项是（　　）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>卖炭翁</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>卖炭翁，伐薪烧炭南山中。满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营？身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歌。翩翩两骑来是谁？黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红绡一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", 